270
00:09:40,447 --> 00:09:42,096
Elyse, we're going
to surgery right now

271
00:09:42,165 --> 00:09:43,764
to take care of
you and your baby.

272
00:09:43,834 --> 00:09:44,933
Okay?

273
00:09:46,185 --> 00:09:47,485
Matthew?

274
00:09:48,021 --> 00:09:49,186
Matthew?

275
00:09:49,255 --> 00:09:50,299
Oh, hi.

276
00:09:50,323 --> 00:09:52,018
