shield a kid from the blast

278
00:09:53,793 --> 00:09:55,743
with his own body.

279
00:09:55,811 --> 00:09:56,955
Well, it seemed like the
right thing to do at the time.

280
00:09:56,979 --> 00:09:58,195
He could've died.

281
00:09:58,264 --> 00:09:59,642
Yeah, but I didn't. I'm... Ow.

282
00:09:59,666 --> 00:10:01,666
I'm fine.

283
00:10:01,735 --> 00:10:02,975
Just go ahead and go.

284
00:10:03,036 --> 00:10:04,647
You got more important
patients than me.

285
00:10:04,671 --> 00:10:07,422
